"block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39866,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/21\/jannah-after-punishment\/","url_meta":{"origin":42699,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Hereafter: Sinful believers enter Paradise after punishment","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 21, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Salamah ibn Nu\u2019aym reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever meets Allah without associating any partners with Him will eventually enter Paradise.\u201d I said, \u201cEven if he commits adultery and theft?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cEven if he commits adultery and theft.\u201d Source: al-Sunnah li-Ibn\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2959,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/19\/major-sins-shirk-kadhib-murder\/","url_meta":{"origin":42699,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Major Sins: Worst are idolatry, murder, false witness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 19, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said regarding the major sins, \u201cThey are associating partners with Allah, disrespect to parents, killing someone, and false testimony.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5977, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 88 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","co